{"tid":1704283,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實大家宜家應該去叫政府交代，唔係到處破壞","createTime":"2019-11-10T15:37:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T15:59:07.000Z","uid":338306,"like":0,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9c9a7b9e4ec2a661d22952823b66fc60017e7e0b","tid":1704283,"uid":338306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:37:56.000Z","msg":"經歷咁多日，大家都好似得唔到政府有一d回應，每個禮拜日就係各區有遊行活動，但係其實政府好似唔多想理，反而影響到好多香港市民，其實令到好多市民反感。不如唔好破壞，去政府總部要求政府交代好過，每個禮拜見到係示威衝突裡面有人受傷我都覺得好心痛，我覺得香港唔應該咁㗎！無論係大家政見如何，大家都係香港人，唔應該自己人打自己人㗎，明知有唔正義嘅事發生，香港人應該要更加團結，對抗唔合理唔正義嘅政策。經過呢幾個月，我都覺得好煩躁，所以想po出黎發洩下情緒。"},{"pid":"e0dc600dc4b49624e1f181e76f902a0fe7c9e6b8","tid":1704283,"uid":126621,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:39:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jM9yEVS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjM9yEVS.gif&h=36baf129&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\non9<br />\n政府肯交代<br />\n就唔洗搞五個月啦<br />\n<br />\n俾我做特首 一日搞撚店啦"},{"pid":"40b360b5d4c236646dacbf5f00c6cef5c6d94db9","tid":1704283,"uid":147952,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:40:46.000Z","msg":"師兄衰咩？啱啱先放返出嚟？"},{"pid":"cf6a18591242ec5b725de3e5b2b904a97d78b062","tid":1704283,"uid":96465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:41:25.000Z","msg":"ON9仔"},{"pid":"c219f27d7335aa313fcce549cad3c8e2728c3457","tid":1704283,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:41:50.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"d874943014626ddada45632cb61b63065aa9541b","tid":1704283,"uid":99365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:41:58.000Z","msg":"請善用不推文回覆"},{"pid":"6fc4e2d0115f5964bc63b77f57a6c006ac8135aa","tid":1704283,"uid":18628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:43:49.000Z","msg":"係都要衝出黎比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcbf9d519b20f198eea812f6856af48730a04334","tid":1704283